{"session_id": 49, "bill_id": 15649, "bill_type": "House Bill", "bill_number": 1246, "bill_title": "exempt certain transfers of property used for agricultural or business purposes from the inheritance tax.", "sponsors": [{"legislator_profile_id": 2376, "is_prime": true}, {"legislator_profile_id": 2377, "is_prime": true}, {"legislator_profile_id": 2318, "is_prime": false}, {"legislator_profile_id": 2326, "is_prime": false}, {"legislator_profile_id": 2332, "is_prime": false}, {"legislator_profile_id": 2342, "is_prime": false}, {"legislator_profile_id": 2344, "is_prime": false}, {"legislator_profile_id": 2353, "is_prime": false}, {"legislator_profile_id": 2390, "is_prime": false}, {"legislator_profile_id": 2403, "is_prime": false}, {"legislator_profile_id": 2408, "is_prime": false}], "keywords": ["Inheritance Tax"], "audio": [{"meeting_datetime": "2000-02-10T00:00:00-06:00", "committee": "H", "url": "https://sdpb.sd.gov/sdpbpodcast/2000/hou23hb1246a.mp3", "start_seconds": 0.0}, {"meeting_datetime": "2000-02-10T00:00:00-06:00", "committee": "H", "url": "https://sdpb.sd.gov/sdpbpodcast/2000/hou23hb1246a.mp3", "start_seconds": 0.0}], "bill_versions": [{"bill_id": 15649, "bill_version_id": 86565, "bill_version": "Introduced", "bill_version_date": "2000-01-21T00:00:00-06:00", "bill_text": "FOR AN ACT ENTITLED, An Act to exempt certain transfers of property used for agricultural or business purposes from the inheritance tax. BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF SOUTH DAKOTA: Section 1. That \u00a7 10-40-23 be amended by adding thereto a NEW SUBDIVISION to read as follows: An additional value not to exceed five hundred thousand dollars of real property or business property, if the property is transferred from a decedent to lineal issue of the decedent and if the real property is agricultural land, defined pursuant to \u00a7 10-6-31.3, or business property as, defined pursuant to subdivision 10-45-1(2). This exemption is applicable if the decedent was the majority owner which was transferred at the time of the decedent's death. The value of this exemption shall be prorated among the lineal issue of the decedent who have inherited or received the property. This exemption is in addition to the exemption provided in subdivision (3) of this section. Section 2. For the purposes of this Act, a majority interest, in the applicable exempt property shall be computed by including, as of the date of the decedent's death, all of the decedent's ownership interest, the decedent's spouse's ownership interest, the ownership interest of any lineal issue, and the ownership interest of any trust which has been created by the decedent, the decedent's spouse, or lineal issue. Section 3. The provisions of this Act do not apply to any inheritance that results from the death of a decedent prior to January 1, 2001."}], "amendments": [], "fiscal_notes": [], "action_log": [{"bill_id": 15649, "action_date": "2000-01-21T14:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 85636, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/85636.pdf", "status_text": "First read in House and referred to", "journal_page": 179, "committee_id_action": 656, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "N", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 15649, "action_date": "2000-01-24T14:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 85638, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/85638.pdf", "status_text": "Referred to", "journal_page": 206, "committee_id_action": 656, "committee_id_assigned": 652, "result": "P", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 15649, "action_date": "2000-01-27T07:45:00-06:00", "document_id": 85791, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/85791.pdf", "status_text": "Scheduled for Committee hearing on this date", "journal_page": null, "committee_id_action": 652, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "N", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 15649, "action_date": "2000-02-08T07:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 85876, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/8